  <div class="views-field views-field-FM-26">    <div class="views-label views-label-FM-26 field-label">Physical: </div>    <span class="field-content">Public outdoor covered place where people can gather.<br><div style="height: 5px;"></div></span>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-FM-30">    <div class="views-label views-label-FM-30 field-label">Broader: </div>    <span class="field-content"><a title="Context boundary" href="12610150">Context boundary</a><br><a title="Context for disorder" href="12610580">Context for disorder</a><br><a title="Local action network" href="12610450">Local action network</a><br><a title="Accessible non-linearity" href="12610600">Accessible non-linearity</a><br><a title="Principal points of entry" href="12610530">Principal points of entry</a><br><a title="Unstructured common domain" href="12610670">Unstructured common domain</a><br><a title="Bounded common small-scale interaction domains" href="12610610">Bounded common small-scale interaction domains</a><br><a title="Cyclic interrelation of complementary perspective in common domains" href="12610630">Cyclic interrelation of complementary perspective in common domains</a><br></span>  </div>  
